Key Match Events: Taskin Ahmed dismissed Vikramjit Singh and Bas de Leede off consecutive deliveries in the first two balls of the Dutch team's run-chase
Hasan Mahmud and Mustafizur Rahman also played their roles with precision
Post-Match Reflections: Taskin Ahmed said that he hoped to take a hat-trick but missed out due to a lack of luck
Taskin mentioned that hitting the hard lengths on a consistent basis helped the Bangladesh fast bowlers
